## Product [/product/]

### Retrieve single variation (aka product) [POST]

To retrieve a single prodtuct.
Retrieving a single product requires 
a JSON object containing the model slug,
collection name and product ID.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "model": "day2",
            "collection": "Earth",
            "id": 67955
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /product/

    + Body

            {
                "model": "day2",
                "collection": "Earth",
                "price": 999,
                "sku": "500030",
                "variation": [
                    {
                        "id": 67955,
                        "pa_bekleding": "Hippo grey",
                    },
                ],
                "cart_link": "/cart/?configurator=true&add-to-cart=67955&user-hash=xxx",
            }